definitions.definition: A small spring , pool , or other spot where liquid from the ground (e.g. water , petroleum or tar ) has oozed to the surface; a place of seeping.
Moisture , liquid , gas , etc. that seeps out; a seepage .
The seeping away of a liquid, etc.
